title: Goblins (Web Comic) - Books 1 through 4 {WebComixFan}
description:
"Goblins" Web Comic

"Goblins" (goblinscomic.org) by Tarol Hunt ("Thunt") Stephens is set in a humorously stereotypical fantasy setting and follows the lives of a party of goblin adventurers who started as monsters but later declared themselves player characters.  The tagline for the comic, "Life Through Their Eyes," reflects the predominant theme of the comic, telling a heroic tale of creatures normally viewed only as evil and weak.  The comic often contains scenes of strong violence.

This torrent includes books 1 through 4 of Thunt's Web comic, "Goblins," in CBR format.  Book 1 includes comics from 2005 and 2006, book 2 from 2006 and 2007, book 3 from 2007 through 2009, and book 4 from 2009 through 2012.  I haven't included more recent comics as book 5 isn't yet complete.  Note that these are NOT the official e-books; all the comics in this torrent were downloaded directly from the goblinscomic.org Web site
